  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manwoody\" title=\"House Manwoody\"><img alt=\"House Manwoody.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/50px-House_Manwoody.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/75px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/100px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Dagos Manwoody</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manwoody\" title=\"House Manwoody\"><img alt=\"House Manwoody.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/50px-House_Manwoody.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/75px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/100px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"AurelienHubert Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d3/AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg/300px-AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d3/AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg/450px-AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d3/AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg/600px-AurelienHubert_Oberyn-s-Bannerman.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Aurelien Hubert © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Kingsgrave\" title=\"Lord of Kingsgrave\">Lord of Kingsgrave</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Manwoody\" title=\"House Manwoody\">House Manwoody</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Manwoody\" title=\"Mors Manwoody\">Mors Manwoody</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Manwoody\" title=\"Dickon Manwoody\">Dickon Manwoody</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dagos Manwoody</b> is the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsgrave\" title=\"Kingsgrave\">Kingsgrave</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manwoody\" title=\"House Manwoody\">House Manwoody</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagos_Manwoody&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagos_Manwoody&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Dagos, accompanied by his brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Manwoody\" title=\"Myles Manwoody\">Myles</a>, and his two sons, <a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Manwoody\" title=\"Mors Manwoody\">Mors</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Manwoody\" title=\"Dickon Manwoody\">Dickon</a>, are part of the entourage of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> when he comes to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to claim the seat <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> had offered the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Dagos is present when Tyrion comes to see Oberyn on the day of his <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a>, helping the prince don his battle armor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagos_Manwoody&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Dagos is present at the feast when Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon Swann</a> arrives in <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> to deliver the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_skull\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s skull\">Mountain's skull</a>. He refuses to drink when <a href=\"/index.php/Ricasso\" title=\"Ricasso\">Ricasso</a> raises a toast to King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagos_Manwoody&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"